== [[Wikibooks:Bots]] ==

[[Wikibooks:Bots]] is now a policy. It was a pretty non-controversial proposal that mostly documented the things that we already do here now, so nothing changes because of this. This proposal purposefully errs on the side of being "too little", and we as a community can update it piecemeal as issues become apparent. There was a branch proposed and opened for voting, although it was more controversial and was raising some concerns. We can certainly continue discussion on the branch, and use points from it to update the new Bots policy as needed. --'''Whiteknight'''&nbsp;([[User:Whiteknight|Page]])&nbsp;([[User talk:Whiteknight|Talk]]) 23:03, 14 November 2008 (UTC)

