:Just start a new page and copy&paste some of the content of the existing page to the new page. Of course, you also have to link the new page appropriately (from the table of contents etc.) I'm not aware of any special functionality for breaking up pages. Hope this helps. --[[User:Martin Kraus|Martin Kraus]] ([[User talk:Martin Kraus|talk]]) 14:42, 23 November 2008 (UTC)

