There isn't an automatic way yet, but if you're going to be creating collections for print and distribution, a little page like this in the front as an explanation would be a big help. --'''Whiteknight'''&nbsp;([[User:Whiteknight|Page]])&nbsp;([[User talk:Whiteknight|Talk]]) 20:08, 5 November 2008 (UTC)

